<!DOCTYPE html> 
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <title>SkillConnect</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Styles */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #FEF7DC; /* Lighter background */
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* Navigation Bar */
        header {
            background-color: #51454e; /* Dark for the navbar */
            padding: 15px 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin: 0;
            color: #FEF7DC; /* Light text for dark navbar */
        }

        header nav {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-right: 3vw;        
        }

        header nav a {
            color: #FEF7DC; /* Light text for contrast */
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0 15px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        header nav a:hover {
            color: #C2B8A3; /* Medium tone for hover */
        }

        /* Main Content */
        main {
            padding: 80px 20px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 60px; /* Ensure content does not hide behind header */
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(118, 116, 118, 0.8), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)), url('/images/hero-bg.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .hero h2 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin: 0 0 20px;
            color: black;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .hero button {
            background-color: rgba(154, 152, 154, 0.8); /* Medium tone for button */
            color: #34322c;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .hero button:hover {
            background-color: #A19882; /* Darker tone for hover */
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .features {
            
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .feature {
            background-color: #E6DDC6; /* Secondary light background */
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 28%;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            color: #34322c;
        }

        .feature:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .feature h3 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #34322c;; /* Dark tone for headings */
        }

        .feature p {
            font-size: 1em;
            color: #666;
        }

        /* Testimonials Section */
        .testimonials {
            background-color: #C2B8A3; /* Medium tone for testimonials */
            padding: 40px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .testimonials h2 {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin: 0 0 20px;
            color: #34322c;; /* Light for contrast */
        }

        .testimonial {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .testimonial p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #666;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .testimonial cite {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-style: normal;
            color: #504d44;
        }

        /* Footer Section */
        footer {
            background-color: #E6DDC6; /* Secondary light background */
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #333; /* Dark for contrast */
            box-shadow: 0 -4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        footer h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #A19882; /* Darker for headings */
        }

        footer p {
            font-size: 1em;
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #333; /* Dark for contrast */
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0 10px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            color: #A19882; /* Dark for hover */
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .feature {
                width: 100%;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to SkillConnect!</h1>
        <nav>
            <% if (user) { %>
                <p>Hello, <%= user.username %>!</p>
                <a href="/search_people">People</a>
                <a href="/search">Showcases</a>
                <a href="/post">Post</a>
                <a href="/profile">Profile</a>
                <a href="/logout">Logout</a>

            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/">Home</a> | <a href="/login">Login</a> | <a href="/register">Register</a> | <a href="/about">About Us</a>
            <% } %>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <h2>Connect with Skilled Professionals</h2>
            <p>Whether you're looking to hire experts or offer your skills, SkillConnect is the perfect platform for you.</p>
            <% if (!user) { %>
                <button onclick="window.location.href='/register'">Get Started</button>
            <% } %>
        </section>

        <section class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>For Skill Seekers</h3>
                <p>Find the right professionals for your needs. Browse portfolios, check ratings, and hire with confidence.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>For Skill Providers</h3>
                <p>Showcase your skills, connect with potential clients, and grow your freelance business.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Secure and Reliable</h3>
                <p>Our platform ensures safe transactions and protects your personal information.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="testimonials">
            <h2>What Our Users Say</h2>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"SkillConnect has transformed the way I find freelance opportunities. The platform is user-friendly and effective."</p>
                <cite>- Alex R., Skill Seeker</cite>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"As a skill provider, Iâ€™ve been able to showcase my expertise and connect with great clients. Highly recommend!"</p>
                <cite>- Jamie L., Skill Provider</cite>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"The secure and reliable nature of SkillConnect makes it a go-to platform for both freelancers and clients."</p>
                <cite>- Taylor M., Platform User</cite>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>